Variant: gui

Normal               white               black
Terminal             white               black
CursorLine           omit                black
StatusLineTerm       white               royalpurple       bold
StatusLineTermNC     gray                royalpurple       bold

Variant: gui 256 8

; Group              Foreground          Background        Attributes
ColorColumn          omit                black
Cursor               fg                  truegreen
CursorColumn         omit                black
CursorLineNr         omit                black             bold
FoldColumn           none                black
Folded               white               royalpurple
IncSearch            white               royalpurple
LineNr               gorod               none              bold
Search               white               truegreen
StatusLine           white               royalpurple       bold
StatusLineNC         gray                royalpurple       bold
Visual               fg                  royalpurple

Comment              aqua          none
Constant             lightorchid         none
Error                lightgray           burntorange
Identifier           pink                none              t=bold
Ignore               black               none
PreProc              blue                none
Special              green               none
Statement            gorod               none              g=bold
Type                 lightgreen          none              g=bold
Underlined           lightblue           none              underline

lCursor              -> Cursor

ToolbarLine          white               black
ToolbarButton        white               royalpurple       bold

; }}}
